request URL: protocol://location/path/file.ext

input/output
----------------------------------------------
  - io
    + file
      - file open/close
      - file descriptor read/write
      - extension
    + http
      - socket open/close
      - file descriptor read/write
      - extension

file extension
----------------------------------------------
  - extension
    + wav (container format)
      - handle container header
      - format
    + mp3
      - format

data format
----------------------------------------------
  - format
    + pcm
      - big/little endian
      - floats
      - compressed
      - integer
        - signed/unsigned 
    + mp3
      - raw
